{"tid":595892,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"90s' Whatsapp Group","createTime":"2018-03-17T06:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T11:33:59.000Z","uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b01740e88c4d534314689a091728ada8442faacb","tid":595892,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"時移世易 90s' Whatsapp Group 乃 18至22 Whatsapp Group延續。 <br />\n<br />\n我們希望關系和諧，因始沒有你我之分，更沒有兩登之分。<br />\n<br />\n90s' Whatsapp Group 建立兩周年並開放網址供內部使用，可能係第一個擁有自己網站嘅群組*。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前填過嘅可以在填多次 順便睇睇張Form嘅聲明及條款細則<br />\n<br />\n張Form會開到3月24日 填form後兩星期內如有幸抽中會有專人通知入Group <br />\n多謝各位一路以來既支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://watashi.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwatashi.hk%2F&d=fZM7N6QrlwatQABWD2VYM9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=ed5a030b\" target=\"_blank\">http://watashi.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n90s' Whatsapp Group 為會員而設，暫時只限相關會員加入。謝謝！。<br />\n<br />\n***為確保言論自由不被惡意功擊/侵犯及Group內成員及相關私穩，請填寫表格前細閱所有聲明條款及細則***<br />\n<br />\n再次感謝各位一年來的支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">*90s' Whatsapp Group網站只供內部使用及受條款細則約束</span>"},{"pid":"8f3050b2a1d8f25260a83b3e3f9e11d7b782a062","tid":595892,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171b721a1a22a8fd03f82b78b48ed990711ad6d1","tid":595892,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27cd5a4a676e54077a1351cc72a9fb7ac11f86c","tid":595892,"uid":53331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53cc843c59ba7fe5170c1586e